name: Eddy
overview: Eddy is a simple single-screen platformer with puzzle elements in which you play the titular character of Eddy. The goal of the game is to collect all the pots/bags of money before the timer runs out. There are also skulls which you must avoid or jump over. If you hit a skull, then you lose a life. The game was developed by Joachim Rese and published as a type-in game by Tronic Verlag GmbH in Compute mit 1986/06.
